  "raw_text": "Everything that calls itself not the Empire is the Empire. 2) Everything that calls itself Xtianity is not Xtianity. 3) It is in fact the Empire. 4) The true church (as Luther said) is persecuted, hidden + poor (+, I would add, at the periphery vis-a-vis worldly power, as it was at the time + place of Acts). Then this is why Acts + USA 1974 are 2 sets of appearances sharing a common essence. Both contain all the same ingredients, but topologically there is complete reversal in each feature, when you compare one set to the other. + Acts is true; + USA 1974 is a simulation that is a reversal of what is the case, feature by feature [...] {folder 01 - 114} Yes, I am right; I meta-abstracted to a common essence for the two. But set/groung are reversed between them. There is topological correspondence, but USA 1974 is Acts pulled inside out + vice versa, with all value signs reversed! This bears a striking resemblance to the Gnostics' insistence that the O.T. must be read \"inside out\", with all the '+' signs turned to '-' signs + vice versa. So I'm back to Gnostic Xtianity: \"the secret stolen...\" etc. USA 1974 + Acts are exactly the same thing - but with polarities reversed. So of course they derive from a common eidos; it's a matter of \"reading\" the equation in terms of its value signs. This is frankly the very gist if what is meant by the Gnosis, this esoteric reversal of value signs in the \"narrative\". Satan becomes Christ; Xtianity becomes the Empire; etc. So seeing USA 1974 as Acts amounts to a revelation/perception of set/ground reversal. Sudden + complete. This is a familiar phenomenon in figure-ground perception (in Gestalt psychology. + I am an absolute Gestalting organism!) Now becomes then; here becomes there. {folder 01 - 115} Victor in history becomes loser: viz: \"Xtianity defeated Rome\" becomes \"Rome defeated Xtianity\". Hence we wind up with such clues as \"the church's prisons\" + \"the imperial church\". 1) I meta-abstracted. + 2) I did a figure-ground value reversal (which equals the Gnostic esoteric Gnosis; which comes as revelation). So there was more to it than meta-abstracting. I saw that the common essence could be read two different -opposite- ways [Note]. + the exoteric way I'd been doing it was precisely the wrong way. [Note] The 2 sets of appearance. That puts Christ in the trash stratum exactly as in \"Ubik\". + the metamorphosis of Ubik in the last chapter heading is a figure-ground reversal. + this is also enantiodromia - maybe the ultimate one in terms of world perception. That's what that terrible (recent) dream about the book I should write listing the death camp victims + how they died - packaged as a book of eroticism; eros masking thanatos. I.e. Value signs reversal, with thanatos as the truth. This indubitably equates Gnosticism with the RC enlightenment. I'm too tired to explicate, but trust me. {folder 01 - 116} Enlightenment is clandestine, perforce. I was right when I sensed 3-74 at the time as R.C. Now I see the Gnostic-Catharist-R.C. connection + the suppression of knowledge by Xtianity (the Empire) vs the secret societies + true esoteric Xtianity: all the value signs reversed. There is a secret Xtian true church: + it is R.C. Based on the Gnostic \"backward-read interpretation\" method: things are precisely the opposite of what they seem, + Acts is a sort of metaphor for the true state of affairs (rather than having to do with literal space + time; it is an eidos reinterpreted. [illustration presented below in text format] + Acts USA 1974 - I I eidos Acts is USA 1974 with the value signs corrected, i.e. reversed. Space + time have nothing to do with it; it's a matter of figure-ground. That's why the 2 sets of accidents syntonically superimposed. It has to do with perception + reversed perception i.e. corrected perception. So to find God you look in the trash + the alley - not upwards to the firmament. Just as \"Ubik\" has it! What is truly amazing (besides the fact that 2-3-74 is in itself truly amazing) is that there is a mysterious {folder 01 - 117} still small voice in the night that tells one -me- the truth of the situation. If you consider this + then work back to the situation from the voice, you get something like \"the servant has become the master + the master the servant\" + the talking horse's head - + you find when you add 2-3-74 to the existence of the voice - well, you find yourself faced with a situation of total deception, of diabolic reversal between \"is\" + \"seeming\". + in this respect you have the 2 level reality of my 10 volume meta novel. Now, what does \"the secret stolen\" imply? Indeed the Gnostic view of a conspiracy at the highest level to enslave + delude us; the story of the revolt in heaven is recast with the value signs reversed! + you have man sinless - the idea of sinful man + esp. original sin is a lie, an enslaving lie [Note] - + the Fall due to our taking the spatiotemporal world as real; + it was designed to delude us by its creator. It has a dim intelligence (the lesser horn of the dialectic). (Against whom Christ fights.) 2-3-74 becomes the revelation of the secret truth (i.e. the Gnosis), not just the real truth. [Note] + Heimarmene is a retributive + totally soulless + cruel machine that the Messenger saves us from - e.g. me vis-a-vis the Xerox Missive. {folder 01 - 118} Then epistemologically speaking what I realized in 2-74 was that our spatiotemporal world is not real (as well as being enslaving); + the actual truth is a mirror opposite of it - including the fact, later revealed to me, of another world that is real (the Macrometasomakosmos). It is not real, but is only a set of aspects or \"seemings\"; here is Gnostic acosmism, with the AI voice verifying what I realized. \"Time, the counterfeit of eternity\". So more than just sign reversal is pointed to by USA 1974 fading out + Acts fading in. Irreality of the spatiotemporal world is pointed to. + esp. an actual deluding semireality. But I see the sacred as the ostensible, the profane world, turned inside out. With everything reversed topologically, as in \"Ubik\" - + I don't think the Gnostics taught this. This is even more of a mystery than the Gnostic idea of God being the totally other, alien to this world. You turn USA 1974 inside out + you get not only Acts (value sign reversal) but, as if the trash layer is now viewed inside out - viewed properly - you get God; trash is seen as the divine power itself, not then nor there but here + now. Hence I said, \"I've always seen the universe backward\" + \"I am no longer blind!\" + the universe of plurality becomes a living unity: became what I call Valis (just as in \"Ubik\". So again I have an original system with my two levels of reality. {folder 01 - 119} Is this the real Gnostic secret? \"Break a stick, lift a rock, + there am I [Christ].\"? The real world, the sacred world, is invisibly exploded in our irreal world right here. This is why I had the surd left over in my exegesis. The final mystery had not been explained, that of the theophany itself, Valis. Turn the profane (+ irreal) world inside out + you get God. \"I define God as world [i.e. reality] under the threat of death.\" Seen as we see it (i.e. world) it is both irreal + mundane (profane, trash). Reverse it topologically + you get - well, ultimately it is God. But not exactly world is God but an irreal world is a smokescreen - in itself unreal - concealing God who is real. The process that ends up in your finding God is a series of reversals. An epistemological labyrinth. \"The workman is invisible within the workshop.\" \"God is as close to you as your neckvein.\" Sufism? In sequence: 1) All value signs reversed 2) World as irreal. (the spatiotemporal) 3) Morphologically arranged world not in time + space. 4) God. Like cosmogony running backward. Well, yes; time, too is reversed. 1) First flipflop y to y 2) Then y to -y, which is not y ! {folder 01 - 120} You reverse the reversal but you don't get ostensible world back (USA 1974); you get God. It's layer after layer of ascending ontology. Plotinus? Is the original Fall - due to an epistemological error - being reversed in the sequence in which it happened? So I'm back to Neo-Platonism! 1) USA 1974 is reversed to 2) become Acts 3) then it is shown that USA 1974 + Acts are aspects of a common non-spatiotemporal essence: the morphologically-arranged Form world. 4) But this gives way to Valis or Ubik or God, + all these reversals occur right here. Gnosticism is dead wrong in certain basic respects, + Neo-Platonism lacks something to do with deception + Dokos. + neither sees the flux world as the servant of the Form world, completing it by feeding into it. Therefore neither system can be said to be correct, + I am back to the Cosmic Christ - + a whole new epistemological-ontological system based on him underlying ostensible reality. He is right here. This is the final secret. What we see that we call \"world\" is not world at all, + it can be forced through a series of reversals each more real than the previous level-situation. {folder 01 - 121} Is the secret connected with time + the reversal of time? Cosmic resorption? I am right in my writing: reality is a series of Chinese boxes, a box within a box within a box, etc.: but a final point comes + you have Valis, but what + who Valis is I have no idea. The Tao, YHWH, Cosmic Christ, Brahman, Shiva, Krishna, or a quantum mechanics phenomenon. Or Ruah, the spirit of God breathing creation into existence out of nothing - ex nihilo; you finally wind up with: non-being -the is-not- is real, + the \"is\" is only seeming, is not real. You open box after box + ascend the levels of being (esse, substantia, einai) + then you open the last one + it contains - nothing! + yet you're faced with the mystery or paradox that Ho On (for want of a better term) is actually right here + now, in the very trash at hand, not far away at all - the ultimate paradox in terms of your long search through level after level of being - he is at the initial least real (sic) level. You wind up back where you started, paradoxically. But now you know that this utterly worthless trash level -mere appearance- is somehow also Ho On, whom you seek. \"The Buddha is a piece of toilet paper.\" \"The Savior is a crushed beer can in the alley.\" Could this be the final great enantiodromia? {folder 01 - 122} So if you push essence far enough in terms of ascending levels, you find you have gone a full circle, + you wind up encountering ultimate deity cooking + riding pop tunes on the radio + popular novels, + a breath of wind in the weeds in the alley. It's as if the ultimate mystery is that there is no mystery - it's like what Robert Anton Wilson says in \"The Cosmic Trigger\" about being outside the castle when you think you're in, + inside it when you think you're out. + in a way what is most paradoxical is that I said it all in \"Ubik\" years ago! So in a way my exegesis of 2-3-74 says only, \"'Ubik' is",
