    {
      "text": "{folder 01 - 113}\n\n612\n\nIn other words, Acts + USA 1974 are mirror opposites of each other in all respects! Acts is USA 1974 turned inside out. Literally. That is what Acts is, + that is what \"Tears\" tells. Overtly + cryptically, \"Tears\" says \"Everything that seems the case is in fact not the case + vice versa.\" Hence when I was no longer blind I said, \"I am seeing the universe inside out; up to now I'd been seeing it backward\" - i.e. reversed, as in a mirror. 1) Everything that calls itself not",
      "matched_alias": "Luther",
      "term_id": "TERM_luther",
      "term_name": "Luther",
      "term_slug": "luther"
    }
